    <description>## Reaper suggestion by myself, N9neLives and SkallyCat:

**A:**
If somebody attacks the Reaper on a night that he&#39;s immune costing him a soul, they are unable to talk the following day.

AND/OR

**B**
If the Reaper attacks an immune player, they are unable to talk the following day.

&gt; Notifications:

&gt; **A:**
**Reaper Target:**
_&quot;Something startled you last night. You&#39;ve been silenced.&quot;_
**Reaper:**
_&quot;Your victim was immune, you&#39;ve silenced them instead.&quot;_

&gt; **B:**
**Attacker:**
_&quot;You were startled upon visiting your target. You&#39;ve been silenced.&quot;_
**Reaper:**
_&quot;Somebody attacked you last night, you&#39;ve silenced them.&quot;_</description>
    
